name: Congenital Misery
description:
Being in your comfort zone, and feeling proudly of your ability to make decisions, just know that somewhere else on this planet, some children are born as the victims of determinism. A doomed determinism following them from their initiations, from the very beginning of their lives that promises them a life in the shadow of death. Live but not alive.

This work has been dedicated to them, to the people who seem invisible to the governments' eyes, to the people who die every moment, to those who are being removed by the force of determinism.
